     <div type="author_to_the_reader">
   <head>BEDE TO THE READER.</head>
   <p>All vnto whom this storie of our nation shall come, either
hearing it or reading it, I humbly beseche, that for my infirmi<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tes
as well of body as of minde, they wil be intercessours before
the heauenly clemencie. And that euery one in his countre
will so awnswere my labour with mutuall charite, that whereas
I haue noted in euery prouince, shere, or countie, and in the
most notable places thereof, such thinges as I thought worth
the remembraunce, and pleasaunt to the inhabitants of eche
one, that I may for al reward haue the helpe of their godly pra<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>iers.</p>
   <trailer>FARE WELL.</trailer>
</div>
